as a user i enter the website or the application then i follow this steps.
1 : sign in or sign up page
2 : then login page 
3 : personal information to the profile such as address and categaories of product i like .
4 : now look at the search bar top in the home page .
5 : search for the required product .
6 : now select the product
7 : put it to the cart 
8 : open the cart and proceed 
9 : now i will get the payment page .
10 : make the payment and proceed with the order
11 : finalize the address given in the before page 
12 : now click on place the order and u will recive the aknowldgement
13 : exit the application.
